summary: This document appears to be a Metropolitan Correctional Center lieutenant's log and daily activity report for August 10, 2019, the day Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell. It is marked as confidential and originates from the SDNY.

events.title: Daily Activity Log Entry
events.description: A lieutenant's log and daily activity report was generated for the Metropolitan Correctional Center on this date.

locations.name: Metropolitan Correctional Center
locations.context: Federal jail where Jeffrey Epstein was held; location of the daily activity log.

keyFacts: The document is a confidential lieutenant's log and daily activity report from the Metropolitan Correctional Center dated August 10, 2019.
Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell at the Metropolitan Correctional Center on the morning of August 10, 2019.
The document is part of the SDNY (Southern District of New York) evidence files related to the Epstein case.
The log's existence is significant for investigations into the circumstances surrounding Epstein's death.
